#checkoutHelper.modal.fade( tabindex='-1' )
    .text-fix.modal-dialog.modal-dialog-centered.modal-lg( role='document' )
        .modal-content
            .modal-header.d-flex.align-items-start
                h4.quick-font.px-3.grn-font Where is my donation item being delivered to?
                button.btn-close.btn-close( type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' aria-label='close' )
            .modal-body.quick-font
                .container
                    .row
                        p.px-3
                            -
                                var name = 'Partner Agency Name: ' + agency.agencyName;
                                var website = 'Website: ' + agency.agencyWebsite;
                                var phone = 'Phone Number: ' + agency.agencyPhone;
                                var address = 'Address (partial for privacy): ' + agency.agencyAddress.city  + ' ' + agency.agencyAddress.state + ' in ' + agency.agencyAddress.country;
                            span.bold-text.grn-font= name
                            br
                            span.bold-text.grn-font= website
                            br
                            span.bold-text.grn-font= phone
                            br
                            span.bold-text.grn-font= address
                            br
                    .row
                        p.px-3
                            | We deliver the kids' wish items to their
                            |
                            span.org-font managing foster agencies.
                            |
                            | All kids and youth are under our partner foster agencies' care and the
                            | social worker or agency staff will collect the shipped wish items and distribute each gift.
                            | We don't have a drop-off site because we handle all shipping orders to make the donation experience more
                            |
                            span.org-font easy and efficient
                            |
                            | for you. We will notify you with the delivery process.
            .modal-footer
                button.btn.btn-secondary( type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' ) Close

#checkoutHelper2.modal.fade( tabindex='-1' )
    .text-fix.modal-dialog.modal-dialog-centered.modal-lg( role='document' )
        .modal-content
            .modal-header.d-flex.align-items-start
                h4.quick-font.px-3.grn-font Why is there a processing fee?
                button.btn-close( type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' aria-label='close' )
            .modal-body.quick-font
                .container
                    .row
                        p.px-3 We strive not to impose any additional costs on you, given our status as a non-profit organization. However, it's important to note that each card transaction is facilitated through Stripe, a PCI-compliant secure payment processing system. Stripe typically incurs a charge of approximately 3% per transaction.
                    .row
                        p.px-3 Furthermore, to account for potential fluctuations in item prices, we have implemented a 5% cover fee. This ensures that even if the item price increases immediately after your payment, we can still proceed with placing the order and shipping it to the partner agency.
            .modal-footer
                button.btn.btn-secondary( type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' ) Close

#checkoutHelper3.modal.fade( tabindex='-1' )
    .text-fix.modal-dialog.modal-dialog-centered.modal-lg( role='document' )
        .modal-content
            .modal-header.d-flex.align-items-start
                h4.quick-font.px-3.grn-font What is the item sales tax?
                button.btn-close( type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' aria-label='close' )
